        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>COVID-19 Home Safety Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to report, and publish, information about injuries and deaths from consumer products during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency. The report must be submitted every three months for the duration of the emergency.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
